<br>
<br>
Some nitpicking of a previous post:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> I'm sorry, are you asking to form a Nature's Touch rotation on raids? No? Then wtf is your main problem in comprehending this issue? Is your group dying to AE? Then why don't you tell them to get the @#%$ out of the goddamned AE, or get better resist gear, or get off your raid. Please, list all encounters where the AE can not be mitigated by resists, or geometry, or intelligence.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
