<br>
No one here is asking for Druid's to receive 2 second casting, instant recast, 1600 pt heals for 200 mana.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
